9 An Act relating to the Oklahoma Environmental Quality
Code; amending 27A O.S. 2021, Sections 2-14-103, 2-
10 14-301, 2-14-302, 2-14-303, and 2-14-304, which
relate to the Oklahoma Uniform Environmental
11 Permitting Act; modifying definitions; modifying
requirements and procedures for certain
12 notifications; requiring certain information be made
